# Tech stack

- The project is built with React, Next.js, and Tailwind CSS.
- The project uses the following technologies:
  - React
  - Next.js
  - Tailwind CSS
  - Shadcn UI

- Uses npm runtime and package manager
- Uses Vercel for deployment
- Uses PostgreSQL for database (Supabase on Vercel)
- Uses Clerk for authentication
- Uses Stripe for payments
- Uses TypeORM for database modeling

- The app is located in the /app folder, make sure to place all of the React components there.